query:
INSERT INTO products (name, slug, description, price, stockQuantity, categoryId, images, materials, isFeatured, isAvailable, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES
('Burgundy and Pink Two-Tier Earrings', 'burgundy-pink-two-tier-earrings', 'Elegant handmade polymer clay earrings featuring a sophisticated two-tier design. Deep burgundy wine-colored circles sit gracefully atop soft light pink rounded triangles, connected with gold-tone jump rings. These lightweight statement earrings offer a beautiful color contrast that transitions from rich to delicate. Perfect for adding a touch of elegance to any outfit!', 10.00, 5, 1, '[{"url":"https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/mRrdsLNUUzFJdoGx.png"}]', '["Polymer Clay","Gold-tone Jump Rings"]', 1, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Peach Arch Earrings', 'peach-arch-earrings', 'Chic handmade polymer clay earrings in a beautiful peachy coral tone. Features a modern two-tier design with circles on top and unique U-shaped arches below with cutout centers. The soft peach color is versatile and flattering, while the contemporary geometric shape makes a stylish statement. Lightweight and comfortable for all-day wear!', 10.00, 5, 1, '[{"url":"https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/ZUUieTqYnXMhwjnP.png"}]', '["Polymer Clay","Gold-tone Jump Rings"]', 1, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Pink Heart Cactus Earrings', 'pink-heart-cactus-earrings', 'Absolutely adorable handmade polymer clay earrings perfect for cactus and succulent lovers! Features double pink hearts with charming blue cacti topped with pink flowers, plus delicate white pearl dots for extra sweetness. These whimsical earrings bring together nature-inspired design with playful charm. A unique statement piece that is sure to bring smiles!', 15.00, 5, 1, '[{"url":"https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/EWUbuiySpsxFMMfA.png"}]', '["Polymer Clay","Pearls","Gold-tone Jump Rings"]', 1, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Red Rose Statement Earrings', 'red-rose-statement-earrings', 'Stunning handmade polymer clay earrings featuring gorgeous 3D red roses with intricate layered petals. Each rose is carefully crafted to create realistic depth and dimension, paired with sleek black circles on top. These bold statement earrings are perfect for special occasions or adding dramatic flair to everyday outfits. A true showstopper!', 8.00, 5, 1, '[{"url":"https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/IBxMgWlXPqXHOqDT.png"}]', '["Polymer Clay","Gold-tone Jump Rings"]', 1, 1, NOW(), NOW()),
('Pink Pearl Charm Earrings', 'pink-pearl-charm-earrings', 'Delightfully charming mixed-media earrings combining polymer clay, pearls, and adorable enamel charms! Features pink polymer clay circles on top, elegant white pearls in the middle, and sweet gold-tone charms at the bottom - one says "love" in a heart, the other is an adorable pink whale. These playful yet elegant earrings are perfect for anyone who loves whimsical jewelry!', 12.00, 5, 1, '[{"url":"https://files.manuscdn.com/user_upload_by_module/session_file/310519663273273644/poHyfmtScSanDjLY.png"}]', '["Polymer Clay","Pearls","Enamel Charms","Gold-tone Jump Rings"]', 1, 1, NOW(), NOW())
